## Redshift
Redshift database is a cloud based, data warehouse solution offered by Amazon. It provides storage system that stores petabytes of data in easy-to-access clusters. Redshift is based on Postgres 8.0.2 and it supports sql syntax. Support for sql like query language makes it easy to analyze data for different kind of use cases. 

## Pentaho Data Integration
Pentaho Data Integration eliminates coding and complexity, and puts data from any source at the fingertips of business users.  

